THDC India Signs $648 Million World Bank Loan for Hydro Project

-- B y   K a t r i n a   N i c h o l a s
-- 
2011-08-11T02:16:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-11/thdc-india-signs-648-million-world-bank-loan-for-hydro-project.html
THDC India Ltd. signed a $648
million project finance loan due August 2040, according to data
compiled by Bloomberg.  Proceeds will be used to build a hydro electric project in
the South Asian nation, the data show. Monies were provided by
the  World Bank , the data show.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Katrina Nicholas at 
 knicholas2@bloomberg.net  